        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bl-faq-item">
            <h3>{item.q}</h3>
            <p class="aeo-answer">{item.a}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="bl-cta">
        <h2>Planning a golf tournament in Graeagle?</h2>
        <p>Tell us your headcount, format, and dates. We'll send back a full tournament package proposal — tee blocks confirmed, lodging, and banquet options included. Free quote, 24-hour response.</p>
        <a href="/request-a-quote/" class="bl-cta-btn btn-green-glow">Get a Tournament Quote →</a>
        <div class="bl-cta-links">
